-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Infineon, Gamesa, Luxottica 
-- 
-- Thu Oct 23, 2014 02:57AM EDT
-- None



Oct 23 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Infineon and Gamesa, on Thursday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Infineon <IFXGn.DE>: HSBC raises to overweight from neutral; cuts target to 8.9 euros  * Gamesa <GAM.MC>: HSBC raises to overweight from neutral; cuts price target to 9.20 euros * Luxottica <LUX.MI>: Berenberg raises to buy from hold   Following is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Thursday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order. * ABB <ABBN.VX>: SocGen cuts price target to Sfr 21 from Sfr 22; rating hold * BIC <BICP.PA>: Raymond James cuts target to 110 euros from 112 euros; rating outperform * British American Tobacco <BATS.L>: SocGen cuts target to 3350p from 3500p; rating hold * Catalana <GCO.MC>: UBS cuts to neutral from sell * Erste Group <ERST.VI>: SocGen cuts price target to 20 euros from 21 euros; rating hold * Gamesa <GAM.MC>: HSBC raises to overweight from neutral * Gamesa <GAM.MC>: HSBC cuts price target to 9.20 euros from 9.30 euros * Home Retail <HOME.L>: SocGen cuts price target to 156p from 172p; rating sell * Infineon <IFXGn.DE>: HSBC raises to overweight from neutral * Infineon <IFXGn.DE>: HSBC cuts price target to 8.9 euros from 9.6 euros * JCDecaux <JCDX.PA>: Credit Suisse cuts target to 33 euros from 37 euros; rating outperform * Laird Plc <LRD.L>: UBS raises price target to 315p from 300p; rating neutral * Luxottica <LUX.MI>: Berenberg raises to buy from hold * Luxottica <LUX.MI>: Berenberg raises price target to 42 euros from 40 euros * Melexis NV <MLXS.BR>: ING raises price target to 36.50 euros from 34 euros; rating hold * Michelin <MICP.PA>: SocGen cuts price target to 88 euros from 90 euros; rating buy * Nordea <NDA.ST>: UBS raises price target to Sek 95 from Sek 93; rating neutral * Nordex <NDXG.DE>: HSBC raises to neutral from underweight * Nordex <NDXG.DE>: HSBC cuts price target to 13.2 euros from 13.7 euros * Norsk Hydro <NHY.OL>: S&P Capital IQ raises to buy from hold; * Norsk Hydro <NHY.OL>: S&P Capital IQ raises price target to Nok 40 from Nok 38 * PKN Orlen <PKN.WA>: UBS raises price target to Pln 42 from Pln 41; rating neutral * Playtech Plc <PTEC.L>: UBS raises price target to 820p from 780p; rating buy * Porsche <PSHG_p.DE>: UBS cuts price target to 65 euros from 80 euros; rating neutral * Spectris Plc <SXS.L>: UBS cuts price target to 1780p from 2080p; rating neutral  * Stentys <STEN.PA>: SocGen assumes coverage with buy rating; price target 6.80 euros * TNT Express <TNTE.AS>: Berenberg raises to hold from sell * TNT Express <TNTE.AS>: Berenberg cuts price target to 4.90 euros from 5.35 euros * Yara <YAR.OL>: JP Morgan cuts price target to Nok 280 from Nok 285; rating neutral